RelatedSentence: While a NOTA vote is wasted , it seems voters in many small towns of the state chose to do it over choosing smaller parties , independents and even the Aam Aadmi Party .
A whopping 18,489 voters chose the option here .
The constituency had a choice between 14 candidates , including Quasmi Ekta Dal 's Gun Devi .
In fact , it seemed as if across the state , it was en masse rejection of Aam Aadmi Party in constituencies that registered a high number of NOTA votes .
In Kaushambi , where 15,155 voters chose NOTA , AAP 's Swarnlata Suman polled only 3,692 votes .
